body:
To make sure that all logs are written on early startup, we should add this code to the early startup phase after logging is fully configured:

```java
Stream.of(MMapDirectory.class, VectorUtil.class).forEach(cls -> {
 try {
  Class.forName(cls.getName());
 } catch (ReflectiveOperationException re) {
  throw new SolrException(...)
 }
});
```

Maybe add a TODO to use `MethodHandles.lookup().ensureClassInitialized` in Solr 10 w/ Java 17:

```java
final var lookup = MethodHandles.lookup();
Stream.of(MMapDirectory.class, VectorUtil.class).forEach(cls -> {
 try {
  lookup.ensureInitialized(cls);
 } catch (ReflectiveOperationException re) {
  throw new SolrException(...)
 }
});
```
